{"tid":1556391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好吹「願榮光歸香港」係國歌住","createTime":"2019-09-09T16:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T19:06:09.000Z","uid":81236,"like":82,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8572c619db7cec08401dc23f6b6f87900d9086","tid":1556391,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:55:47.000Z","msg":"無錯「係住」<br />\n<br />\n因為我地而家爭取緊既係五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n但呢首絕對係一首係香港既民主自由之歌！<br />\n係一首軍歌！<br />\n係一首只有香港人同幫香港爭取民主自由既地方敢播既歌！<br />\n係一首屬於香港人時代革命之歌！<br />\n<br />\n我唔反對日後有機會佢會成為獨立之歌<br />\n<br />\n但以呢首歌向國際宣傳香港對民主自由既追求絕對比宣傳為香港國歌既影響力更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd4da1fd045b7c6aa818d206fde2507c9206fe7","tid":1556391,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:56:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNn6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=ecc3b49d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a>"},{"pid":"8c6092f55bc9a4b3c932cc52a06f23a858faf406","tid":1556391,"uid":2904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:02:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[全民和你唱]</span></span> 全世界全天候街邊唱香港國歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556100</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc2cba3d6a4f68fdb1b0f289d86a551a55b022e4","tid":1556391,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0847e6540a33bde10da5f007111135fee4fc6b32","tid":1556391,"uid":251292,"like":8,"dislike":11,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"國歌就國歌<br />\n洗乜怕講"},{"pid":"03b03aca50388e5b732ffcda5bb54cff15fc865c","tid":1556391,"uid":126438,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":